query:
WITH entities AS (
            SELECT * 
            FROM core_fiscal_years
            WHERE chart_id = $1 
            AND year = $2
            ) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $3 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_fiscal_year_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.id, e.sequence
